Setting up machine:

    install node.js
        download from site

    install angular cli
        # npm install -g @angular/cli

    when creating apps
        ng new <project name>
        flags:
            --no-strict
            --standalone boolean - standalone project build
            --routing boolean - routing

    when running this project build command got a question about sharing pseudonymous with Google, saying no for right now
        read https://angular.io/analytics for more info

    Askes about stylesheet format: selecting CSS
    Askes about Server-Side Rednering and Static Site Generation: selecting No

    once the build of the project cd into project folder
    to "run" the application

        ng serve 